-- Tepco Plans to Invest in Coal-Fired Power Plant in Vietnam, Nikkei Reports
-- Bill Koenig
-- 2010-06-21T17:06:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/tepco-plans-to-invest-in-coal-fired-power-plant-in-vietnam-nikkei-reports.html

          
          
             Tokyo Electric Power Co., also known
as Tepco, plans to invest in a coal-fired power plan in Vietnam,
Nikkei English News reported, without saying how it got the
information.  
 Tepco may sign today a memorandum of understanding with
Vietnam Oil and Gas Corp., Nikkei said.  
          
          


  


        